        <h1>The Story of... &#39;Dance with My Father&#39; by Luther Vandross</h1>
    
    
    
        <p class="publish_date">28 April 2024, 19:41 | Updated: 28 April 2024, 19:44</p>
    

    
<figure>
<img loading="lazy" alt="Luther Vandross's Dance with My Father" class="content-image" data-image-catalogue-id="648224" width="660" height="370" src="https://imgs.smoothradio.com/images/648224?crop=16_9&amp;width=660&amp;relax=1&amp;format=webp&amp;signature=CjgWnGGA3LulrWjtJn8JHSvLkpo=" srcset="
                https://imgs.smoothradio.com/images/648224?crop=16_9&amp;width=375&amp;relax=1&amp;format=webp&amp;signature=6ZM-deorRXrWSVn4hx868zEILe0= 375w,
                https://imgs.smoothradio.com/images/648224?crop=16_9&amp;width=420&amp;relax=1&amp;format=webp&amp;signature=igJS_iuA8q3pJJVQXZD57xD3bzg= 420w,
                https://imgs.smoothradio.com/images/648224?crop=16_9&amp;width=660&amp;relax=1&amp;format=webp&amp;signature=CjgWnGGA3LulrWjtJn8JHSvLkpo= 660w" sizes="
                (max-width: 375px) 375px,
                (max-width: 420px) 420px,
                660px" />
<figcaption>
    Luther Vandross&#39;s Dance with My Father.
    <span class="attribution">
        Picture: 
Getty/Luther Vandross


    </span>
</figcaption>
</figure>
<div class="author-details">
<p class="author-details__author">
        
            By Tom Eames
        
    </p>
</div>
