<img alt="Facebook share" src="/assets_v4r/gusto/img/facebook-share.png" />
</a>
<a href="https://twitter.com/intent/tweet?url=www.smoothradio.com%2Ffeatures%2Fthe-story-of%2Fdance-with-my-father-lyrics-meaning-facts-video%2F&amp;text=The+Story+of...+%27Dance+with+My+Father%27+by+Luther+Vandross+%40smoothradio" target="_blank" onclick="gusto.tracking.social('twitter', 'share')">
<img alt="X share" src="/assets_v4r/gusto/img/x-share.png" />
</a>
