</svg>
</button>
</div>
</div>
<p class="paragraph-text">At the 2004 Grammys, when the song won two awards, <a href="/artists/celine-dion/age-husband-boyfriend-children-songs/">Celine Dion</a> performed a live version of the song, and Marx accompanied her on the piano.</p><ul><li><a href="/artists/luther-vandross/celine-dion-dance-with-my-father-grammys/"><strong><span class="underline">The incredible moment Celine Dion supported Luther Vandross with emotional performance at Grammy Awards</span></strong></a></li></ul><p class="paragraph-text">After the performance, Vandross accepted the awards in a videotaped speech.</p>
</li>
</ol>

    
        
    
